            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". In this latest case, surveillance footage shows a group of several thieves break into a showroom, find the keys for several cars, and drive them right out into the parking lot before disappearing into the night.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
